title: Cafe Neto
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Mediterranean, Juice bar, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Kosher, Israeli, Non-veg
description: Serves fish, veg options available. The menu has many marked vegan choices including breakfast, chickpea stew, pasta, grilled "cheese," vegan pizza, salads, shakes, sandwiches. Soy milk and almond milk available for shakes or coffee at no extra charge. Offers shaded seating outside as well as air-conditioned inside seating. Saturday night opens after Shabbat ends.
